Maintainer: Nima Hejazi <nh@nimahejazi.org>
Description: Construction of nonparametric-efficient inverse probability
    weighted estimators based on estimation of the propensity score via
    undersmoothing over a sequence of regression models based on the highly
    adaptive lasso.
